          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After any of your World Eaters units Activate, until the End step, each enemy unit within 24” of this unit gains the following ability:


Grating: This unit counts as two units for Martial Savagery and, during enemy World Eaters units advance moves, those units may move up to an additional 4” if that move would end within 4” of this unit.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
